      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 10-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
